<title>Multiple Choice</title>
<exercise id="fs-id1167660261866">
<problem id="fs-id1167660287410">
<para id="fs-id1167660303608">Which of the following combinations would most likely contribute to the development of a superinfection?</para>
<list id="fs-id1167662450396" list-type="enumerated" number-style="upper-alpha">
<item>long-term use of narrow-spectrum antimicrobials</item>
<item>long-term use of broad-spectrum antimicrobials</item>
<item>short-term use of narrow-spectrum antimicrobials</item>
<item>short-term use of broad-spectrum antimicrobials</item>
</list>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-id1167660209360">
<para id="fs-id1167657982216">B</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
