<exercise id="fs-id1167660131926">
<problem id="fs-id1167662427315">
<para id="fs-id1167662499431">Which clinical situation would be appropriate for treatment with a narrow-spectrum antimicrobial drug?</para>
<list id="fs-id1167662550707" list-type="enumerated" number-style="upper-alpha">
<item>treatment of a polymicrobic mixed infection in the intestine</item>
<item>prophylaxis against infection after a surgical procedure</item>
<item>treatment of strep throat caused by culture identified <emphasis effect="italics">Streptococcus pyogenes</emphasis></item>
